{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2460,"text":"Before I get to bulk\nof what I have to say,"},{"time":5533,"text":"I feel compelled just to mention\na couple of things about myself."},{"time":9744,"text":"I am not some mystical,"},{"time":12817,"text":"spiritual sort of person."},{"time":15668,"text":"I'm a science writer."},{"time":17720,"text":"I studied physics in college."},{"time":20015,"text":"I used to be a science\ncorrespondent for NPR."},{"time":24073,"text":"OK, that said:"},{"time":26552,"text":"in the course of working\non a story for NPR,"},{"time":29815,"text":"I got some advice from an astronomer"},{"time":32117,"text":"that challenged my outlook,"},{"time":34248,"text":"and frankly, changed my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37192,"text":"You see, the story was about an eclipse,"},{"time":39408,"text":"a partial solar eclipse\nthat was set to cross the country"},{"time":43976,"text":"in May of 1994."},{"time":46351,"text":"And the astronomer -- I interviewed him,"},{"time":48839,"text":"and he explained what was going to happen\nand how to view it,"},{"time":52140,"text":"but he emphasized that, as interesting\nas a partial solar eclipse is,"},{"time":57385,"text":"a much rarer total solar eclipse\nis completely different."},{"time":62499,"text":"In a total eclipse,\nfor all of two or three minutes,"},{"time":65797,"text":"the moon completely blocks\nthe face of the sun,"},{"time":69152,"text":"creating what he described\nas the most awe-inspiring spectacle"},{"time":74416,"text":"in all of nature."},{"time":76760,"text":"And so the advice he gave me was this:"},{"time":80087,"text":"\"Before you die,\" he said,"},{"time":83108,"text":"\"you owe it to yourself\nto experience a total solar eclipse.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":88105,"text":"Well honestly,\nI felt a little uncomfortable"},{"time":90610,"text":"hearing that from someone\nI didn't know very well;"},{"time":93042,"text":"it felt sort of intimate."},{"time":94457,"text":"But it got my attention,\nand so I did some research."},{"time":99005,"text":"Now the thing about total eclipses is,"},{"time":101076,"text":"if you wait for one to come to you,"},{"time":103486,"text":"you're going to be waiting a long time."},{"time":106902,"text":"Any given point on earth\nexperiences a total eclipse"},{"time":111446,"text":"about once every 400 years."},{"time":115424,"text":"But if you're willing to travel,\nyou don't have to wait that long."},{"time":118950,"text":"And so I learned\nthat a few years later, in 1998,"},{"time":123291,"text":"a total eclipse was going\nto cross the Caribbean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127201,"text":"Now, a total eclipse is visible\nonly along a narrow path,"},{"time":130754,"text":"about a hundred miles wide,"},{"time":132458,"text":"and that's where the moon's shadow falls."},{"time":134576,"text":"It's called the \"path of totality.\""},{"time":136731,"text":"And in February 1998,"},{"time":139178,"text":"the path of totality\nwas going to cross Aruba."},{"time":142649,"text":"So I talked to my husband,\nand we thought: February? Aruba?"},{"time":146989,"text":"Sounded like a good idea anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148732,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149828,"text":"So we headed south,"},{"time":152487,"text":"to enjoy the sun\nand to see what would happen"},{"time":154983,"text":"when the sun briefly went away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157536,"text":"Well, the day of the eclipse\nfound us and many other people"},{"time":160551,"text":"out behind the Hyatt Regency,"},{"time":162756,"text":"on the beach,"},{"time":163943,"text":"waiting for the show to begin."},{"time":165678,"text":"And we wore eclipse glasses\nwith cardboard frames"},{"time":168873,"text":"and really dark lenses that enabled us\nto look at the sun safely."},{"time":173967,"text":"A total eclipse begins\nas a partial eclipse,"},{"time":178226,"text":"as the moon very slowly makes its way\nin front of the sun."},{"time":182026,"text":"So first it looked the sun\nhad a little notch in its edge,"},{"time":186278,"text":"and then that notch grew\nlarger and larger,"},{"time":189423,"text":"turning the sun into a crescent."},{"time":192244,"text":"And it was all very interesting,\nbut I wouldn't say it was spectacular."},{"time":195603,"text":"I mean, the day remained bright."},{"time":197551,"text":"If I hadn't known\nwhat was going on overhead,"},{"time":200585,"text":"I wouldn't have noticed anything unusual."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204052,"text":"Well, about 10 minutes before\nthe total solar eclipse was set to begin,"},{"time":208886,"text":"weird things started to happen."},{"time":211934,"text":"A cool wind kicked up."},{"time":214808,"text":"Daylight looked odd,\nand shadows became very strange;"},{"time":218745,"text":"they looked bizarrely sharp,"},{"time":221003,"text":"as if someone had turned up\nthe contrast knob on the TV."},{"time":225767,"text":"Then I looked offshore,\nand I noticed running lights on boats,"},{"time":229658,"text":"so clearly it was getting dark,"},{"time":232245,"text":"although I hadn't realized it."},{"time":233855,"text":"Well soon, it was obvious\nit was getting dark."},{"time":236152,"text":"It felt like my eyesight was failing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239186,"text":"And then all of a sudden,"},{"time":240984,"text":"the lights went out."},{"time":243830,"text":"Well, at that,"},{"time":245492,"text":"a cheer erupted from the beach,"},{"time":248133,"text":"and I took off my eclipse glasses,"},{"time":250050,"text":"because at this point\nduring the total eclipse,"},{"time":252665,"text":"it was safe to look at the sun\nwith the naked eye."},{"time":256365,"text":"And I glanced upward,"},{"time":260006,"text":"and I was just dumbstruck."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265541,"text":"Now, consider that, at this point,\nI was in my mid-30s."},{"time":270302,"text":"I had lived on earth long enough\nto know what the sky looks like."},{"time":277669,"text":"I mean --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278844,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":279950,"text":"I'd seen blue skies and grey skies"},{"time":283068,"text":"and starry skies and angry skies"},{"time":287033,"text":"and pink skies at sunrise."},{"time":289882,"text":"But here was a sky I had never seen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294317,"text":"First, there were the colors."},{"time":296617,"text":"Up above, it was a deep purple-grey,"},{"time":299606,"text":"like twilight."},{"time":301043,"text":"But on the horizon it was orange,"},{"time":302777,"text":"like sunset,"},{"time":304102,"text":"360 degrees."},{"time":306426,"text":"And up above, in the twilight,"},{"time":309092,"text":"bright stars and planets had come out."},{"time":311541,"text":"So there was Jupiter"},{"time":313167,"text":"and there was Mercury"},{"time":314927,"text":"and there was Venus."},{"time":317090,"text":"They were all in a line."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320528,"text":"And there, along this line,"},{"time":324288,"text":"was this thing,"},{"time":326778,"text":"this glorious, bewildering thing."},{"time":330326,"text":"It looked like a wreath\nwoven from silvery thread,"},{"time":335101,"text":"and it just hung out there\nin space, shimmering."},{"time":340502,"text":"That was the sun's outer atmosphere,"},{"time":344166,"text":"the solar corona."},{"time":345999,"text":"And pictures just don't do it justice."},{"time":348382,"text":"It's not just a ring or halo\naround the sun;"},{"time":352939,"text":"it's finely textured,\nlike it's made out of strands of silk."},{"time":357763,"text":"And although it looked\nnothing like our sun,"},{"time":360288,"text":"of course, I knew that's what it was."},{"time":362566,"text":"So there was the sun,\nand there were the planets,"},{"time":366422,"text":"and I could see how the planets\nrevolve around the sun."},{"time":370477,"text":"It's like I had left our solar system"},{"time":373286,"text":"and was standing on some alien world,"},{"time":375906,"text":"looking back at creation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378779,"text":"And for the first time in my life,"},{"time":381194,"text":"I just felt viscerally connected\nto the universe"},{"time":385240,"text":"in all of its immensity."},{"time":388107,"text":"Time stopped,"},{"time":390387,"text":"or it just kind of felt nonexistent,"},{"time":392959,"text":"and what I beheld with my eyes --"},{"time":396067,"text":"I didn't just see it,"},{"time":398435,"text":"it felt like a vision."},{"time":401858,"text":"And I stood there in this nirvana"},{"time":405530,"text":"for all of 174 seconds --\nless than three minutes --"},{"time":411190,"text":"when all of a sudden, it was over."},{"time":413597,"text":"The sun burst out,"},{"time":414972,"text":"the blue sky returned,"},{"time":416658,"text":"the stars and the planets\nand the corona were gone."},{"time":419859,"text":"The world returned to normal."},{"time":422573,"text":"But I had changed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425619,"text":"And that's how I became an umbraphile --"},{"time":429581,"text":"an eclipse chaser."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430771,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431804,"text":"So, this is how I spend my time\nand hard-earned money."},{"time":436998,"text":"Every couple of years, I head off\nto wherever the moon's shadow will fall"},{"time":442651,"text":"to experience another couple minutes"},{"time":445065,"text":"of cosmic bliss,"},{"time":446549,"text":"and to share the experience with others:"},{"time":448860,"text":"with friends in Australia,"},{"time":450891,"text":"with an entire city in Germany."},{"time":453468,"text":"In 1999, in Munich,\nI joined hundreds of thousands"},{"time":457830,"text":"who filled the streets and the rooftops\nand cheered in unison"},{"time":462615,"text":"as the solar corona emerged."},{"time":465719,"text":"And over time, I've become something else:"},{"time":468498,"text":"an eclipse evangelist."},{"time":471116,"text":"I see it as my job"},{"time":473737,"text":"to pay forward the advice\nthat I received all those years ago."},{"time":479369,"text":"And so let me tell you:"},{"time":482530,"text":"before you die,"},{"time":484787,"text":"you owe it to yourself\nto experience a total solar eclipse."},{"time":489789,"text":"It is the ultimate experience of awe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494781,"text":"Now, that word, \"awesome,\"\nhas grown so overused"},{"time":499388,"text":"that it's lost its original meaning."},{"time":501576,"text":"True awe, a sense of wonder\nand insignificance"},{"time":506079,"text":"in the face of something\nenormous and grand,"},{"time":508634,"text":"is rare in our lives."},{"time":510649,"text":"But when you experience it, it's powerful."},{"time":514484,"text":"Awe dissolves the ego."},{"time":516863,"text":"It makes us feel connected."},{"time":518881,"text":"Indeed, it promotes\nempathy and generosity."},{"time":522920,"text":"Well, there is nothing truly more awesome\nthan a total solar eclipse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528497,"text":"Unfortunately, few Americans\nhave seen one,"},{"time":530906,"text":"because it's been 38 years"},{"time":533150,"text":"since one last touched\nthe continental United States"},{"time":536344,"text":"and 99 years since one last crossed\nthe breadth of the nation."},{"time":541156,"text":"But that is about to change."},{"time":543747,"text":"Over the next 35 years,"},{"time":546854,"text":"five total solar eclipses will visit\nthe continental United States,"},{"time":551162,"text":"and three of them\nwill be especially grand."},{"time":555146,"text":"Six weeks from now, on August 21, 2017 --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":559844,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562547,"text":"the moon's shadow will race\nfrom Oregon to South Carolina."},{"time":567296,"text":"April 8, 2024, the moon's shadow\nheads north from Texas to Maine."},{"time":572723,"text":"In 2045, on August 12,"},{"time":574919,"text":"the path cuts from California to Florida."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579458,"text":"I say:"},{"time":581673,"text":"What if we made these holidays?"},{"time":584288,"text":"What if we --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":585518,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":586570,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590276,"text":"What if we all stood together,"},{"time":595357,"text":"as many people as possible,"},{"time":597457,"text":"in the shadow of the moon?"},{"time":599253,"text":"Just maybe, this shared experience of awe\nwould help heal our divisions,"},{"time":605117,"text":"get us to treat each other\njust a bit more humanely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608918,"text":"Now, admittedly, some folks consider\nmy evangelizing a little out there;"},{"time":614768,"text":"my obsession, eccentric."},{"time":617992,"text":"I mean, why focus so much attention\non something so brief?"},{"time":622896,"text":"Why cross the globe --\nor state lines, for that matter --"},{"time":626622,"text":"for something that lasts three minutes?"},{"time":631165,"text":"As I said:"},{"time":632906,"text":"I am not a spiritual person."},{"time":636006,"text":"I don't believe in God."},{"time":638601,"text":"I wish I did."},{"time":640892,"text":"But when I think of my own mortality --"},{"time":643873,"text":"and I do, a lot --"},{"time":646971,"text":"when I think of everyone I have lost,"},{"time":650575,"text":"my mother in particular,"},{"time":653778,"text":"what soothes me"},{"time":655602,"text":"is that moment of awe I had in Aruba."},{"time":659596,"text":"I picture myself on that beach,"},{"time":662736,"text":"looking at that sky,"},{"time":665037,"text":"and I remember how I felt."},{"time":668661,"text":"My existence may be temporary,"},{"time":671978,"text":"but that's OK because, my gosh,"},{"time":674509,"text":"look at what I'm a part of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":678214,"text":"And so this is a lesson I've learned,"},{"time":680367,"text":"and it's one that applies\nto life in general:"},{"time":683800,"text":"duration of experience\ndoes not equal impact."},{"time":688229,"text":"One weekend, one conversation --\nhell, one glance --"},{"time":693433,"text":"can change everything."},{"time":696508,"text":"Cherish those moments\nof deep connection with other people,"},{"time":700018,"text":"with the natural world,"},{"time":701453,"text":"and make them a priority."},{"time":703216,"text":"Yes, I chase eclipses."},{"time":705654,"text":"You might chase something else."},{"time":707695,"text":"But it's not about the 174 seconds."},{"time":712312,"text":"It's about how they change"},{"time":715024,"text":"the years that come after."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717114,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718308,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}